   visualizations often present a sequence of facts and observations linked
   together by a unifying theme or argument. Narrative visualization in
   immersive environments can provide users with an intuitive experience to
   interactively explore the scientific data, because immersive
   environments provide a brand new strategy for interactive scientific
   data visualization and exploration. However, it is challenging to
   develop narrative scientific visualization in immersive environments. In
   this article, we propose an immersive narrative visualization tool to
   create and customize scientific data explorations for ordinary users
   with little knowledge about programming on scientific visualization.
   They are allowed to define point of interests (POIs) conveniently by the
   handler of an immersive device.
