Abstract = {This paper addresses the use of narrative visualizations as an effective
   way to improve communication, engagement, and knowledge transfer in
   research-practice partnerships (RPPs). I report on the experience of
   developing a narrative visualization reporting research findings to
   educators/school leaders in an RPP focused on providing more equitable
